reviewText: This is more a take show then a movie it hads lots of good information about the paranormal in 3 parts on 3 cds. If your into ghost and paranormal then you will be like me and enjoy it but if your looking for a movie or ghost hunters or ghost adventures this is not the movie for you
The Indigo Child and everything that it entails fascinates me.  This was a broad overview of what the meaning behind such phenomena is.  It implies many things, and effects all things
When you are ready to take the next step with paranormal learning this would be the video I would recommend. I have shared this with several friends and we have all gotten a lot out of it.
